<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ ài wú kě bǐ 迦南110</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ yòng zhǔ de ài yuán liàng wǒ wǒ yòng zhǔ de ài jiē nà nǐ
 wǒ men bǐ cǐ lǐ jiě zūn zhòng xīn huái yào xiàng lán tiān dà hǎi
 ài shì wú kě bǐ de méi yǒu shén me néng qǔ dài
 fán shì bāo róng bù qiú zì jǐ de yì chù ài shì héng jiǔ rěn nài</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
